Third-party components

This repository bundles a precompiled WebAssembly build of the VASM assembler
(static/vasmm68k_motvasm.wasm). VASM is copyright Volker Barthelmann and Frank
Wille and is distributed under its own license (free for personal and
educational use), which is separate from and not covered by the MIT license
above. See <http://sun.hasenbraten.de/vasm/> for its terms.

All other third-party dependencies (Svelte, SvelteKit, Vite, Tailwind CSS,
CodeMirror, Lezer, bits-ui, and the remaining npm packages) are distributed
under the MIT license.
